This paper is primarily focused on industrial IT-security and intrusion detection, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also extensively uses machine learning algorithms for analysis, which suggests that it could also be classified under machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of time series data and analysis techniques also suggests that it could be classified under signal processing (cs.SI) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
